  "texts": [
    "A taxonomy with detailed analysis covers the main knowledge in this field and provides an in-depth introduction to multi-modal tracking models.",
    "• A comprehensive and fair evaluation of popular trackers is conducted on several datasets.",
    "We evaluated 34 methods consisting of 15 RGB-D and 19 RGB-T trackers on five datasets, in terms of accuracy and speed, for various applications.",
    "The advantages and drawbacks of different frameworks were further analyzed in qualitative and quantitative experiments.",
    "• A prospective discussion for multi-modal tracking is provided."
